name: peckish
description: i loooooove love love this piece so much! i ended up doing this for inktober as well, prompt was fruits and all i could think about was that regal, royal stuff you would see in older movies about the greeks feeding grapes to eachother... but instead, lets have some pretty girls do it!! this actually took longer than i thought it was going to and it ended up making me get behind on my inktober prompts, haha. nonetheless, i hope you enjoy it as much as i do!!
